\/umar-not-stop-wife-masajid\/","url_meta":{"origin":13527,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: Umar does not stop his wife from visiting the Masjid","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: One of the wives of Umar attended dawn and evening prayers in congregation in the mosque. It was said to her, \u201cWhy do you go out while you know Umar dislikes it and he is jealous?\u201d She said, \u201cWhat stops him from prohibiting me?\u201d It was said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41148,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/07\/special-hour-friday\/","url_meta":{"origin":13527,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Jumu&#8217;ah: Special hour of prayer on Friday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 7, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn 'Abdillah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe day of Friday is made of twelve hours. No Muslim finds himself supplicating to Allah Almighty during one of them but that Allah will give it to him. Thus, seek it out in the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17474,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/05\/friday-jumuah-prayer-seal-heart\/","url_meta":{"origin":13527,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Friday: Allah seals hearts of those who neglect Friday prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 5, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever hears the announcement of Friday prayer and he does not come, then he hears it again and does not come, then he hears it again and does not come, Allah will place a seal\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28782,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/07\/female-companion-memorize-listening-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":13527,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Female companions learn Quran from the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Hisham bint Harithah reported: I took the chapter, \u201cQaf, by the Glorious Quran,\u201d (50:1) from the mouth of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, on Friday. The Prophet would recite it on the pulpit every Friday. In another narration, she said: The Prophet would pray\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25289,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/increase-dua-prophet-jumuah\/","url_meta":{"origin":13527,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jumu&#8217;ah: Supplications for the Prophet on Friday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIncrease your supplications for me on the day and night of Friday. Wh